name: Clingy
Description: You're a massive people person and you love to help the young, the old, anyone. You love to talk and work in a team. Where there's people, there's you!

name: Control freak
Description: You like to be the boss, you like to communicate (read: tell others what to do) - having power gets you off, basically.

name: Beastmaster
Description: You're beast only in name, but really a softie at heart. You love furry animals and you hug trees. You live for the outdoor, and if you could live outdoor all the time, you would.

name: Oversharer
Description: You take 'sharing is caring' to the next level. There's never too much giving - blood, tears, sweat, goods, gift, food. But that's because you care, and that's ok.

name: Strong silent type
Description: You don't shy away from tough situations. In fact, you thrive in them. You use your strength to help and save others, make the world a better place.

name: Workaholic
Description: Your work ethics is second to none. You're highly commited and want to make an impact in all situations: from life and death situation to the most mundane. No task is too little.

name: Artsy-fartsy
Description: You're nifty and crafty. You're good with hands. You live to feel inspired and you live to inspire others.

name: Corporate slave
Description: Follow the money! Jokes, everything you do here is for free. You give your professional skills to good use. Let them milk you.
